<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/college-logo.svg">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SYCET | Student Fees-Undertaking</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/feesUndertaking.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    
    <div class="mobile-header">
        <div class="toggle">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-bars" id="menubar"></i>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-xmark" id="close-crossbar"></i>
        </div>
        <span class="mobile-title">Fees Undertaking</span>
    </div>

    <div class="main-wrapper">

        <nav class="sidebar" id="sidebar-nav">
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/admin-dashboard" class="sidebar-child active">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-pie"></i></div>
                    <span class="label">Admin Dashboard</span>
                </a>

                <hr style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); margin: 10px 0;">

                <a href="/" class="sidebar-child">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i></div>
                    <span class="label">Registration Form</span>
                </a>
                <a href="/studentUndertaking" class="sidebar-child">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-contract"></i></div>
                    <span class="label">Student Undertaking</span>
                </a>
                <a href="/feesUndertaking" class="sidebar-child">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i></div>
                    <span class="label">Fees Undertaking</span>
                </a>
                <a href="/idCard" class="sidebar-child">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-id-card"></i></div>
                    <span class="label">ID Card</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <main class="content-area">
            <form action="/feesUndertaking" id="submit-Form" method="post" class="paper-form">
                
                <div class="form-header-center">
                    <h1 class="doc-title">UNDERTAKING FOR FEES</h1>
                    <p class="doc-subtitle">(FOR STUDENT)</p>
                </div>

                <div class="text-content fill-in-blanks">
                    <p>
                        I, <input type="text" name="stuname" id="stu-name" class="inline-input long-input" readonly required>
                        son/daughter of <input type="text" name="fathername" id="parent-name" class="inline-input long-input" readonly required>,
                        seeking admission to the <strong>First/Direct Second Year Engineering</strong> in Shreeyash College of Engineering & Technology, Chh. Sambhajinagar for the academic year 2023-2024 in the branch UG: Civil/ Mech/ ETC/ CSE/ AIML/ other, PG: Struct Mech/ CSE/ ETC/ other Engineering.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        I am fully aware that my admission is purely provisional subject to the approval of AICTE, Delhi, DTE Mumbai/ 'PRAVESH NIYANTRAN SMITI', Mumbai. I shall be fully responsible for the consequence thereto.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        I am fully aware and agree that the presently charged fees are interim fees as approved by the 'SHIKSHAN SHULKA SAMITI'/ Authority / Honorable Court/ Hon'ble Supreme Court. 
                        (Interim fees at present Rs <input type="number" name="presentFees" id="fees" class="inline-input short-input" placeholder="0000" autocomplete="off" required> only).
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        I am aware and agree to pay fees which will be finalized by the 'SHIKSHAN SHULKA SAMITI'/ Authority / Honorable Court/ Hon'ble Supreme Court from time to time during my entire period of course and if not paid, I know that my admission will be cancelled for which I will be responsible and I will not hold College/ anybody responsible for cancellation of my admission.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The proposed fees will be about <input type="number" name="praposedFees" id="fees2" class="inline-input short-input" placeholder="0000" autocomplete="off" required>. 
                        I will pay all the fees due on or before submission of the semester till the institution receives all claims for Govt.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <hr class="divider">

                <div class="signature-section">
                    <div class="sign-box">
                        <label>Digital Signature of Student</label>
                        <input type="text" id="stu-name2" class="sign-input" autocomplete="off" readonly required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="sign-box">
                        <label>Digital Signature of Parents</label>
                        <input type="text" id="parent-name2" class="sign-input" autocomplete="off" readonly required>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-grid">
                    <div class="address-box">
                        <label>Address:</label>
                        <textarea name="homeAdress" id="address" rows="3" readonly></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <div class="date-place-box">
                        <div class="form-group-row">
                            <label>Date:</label>
                            <input type="date" name="presentDate" id="date" readonly required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group-row">
                            <label>Place:</label>
                            <input type="text" name="placeName" id="place" placeholder="Enter Place" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="action-buttons">
                    <a href="/studentUndertaking" class="btn btn-secondary">Back</a>
                    <button type="submit" id="disp" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
                    <a href="/idCard" class="btn btn-outline">Next</a>
                </div>

            </form>
        </main>
    </div>

    <script src="/javaScript/thirdpage.js"></script>
</body>
</html>